                   <div class="post hentry">
                    <a name="1494707626336310316">
                    </a>
                    <h3 class="post-title entry-title">
                     Head To LEGOLAND Discovery Center Westchester For A Fun Day Out With The Kids
                    </h3>
                    <div class="post-header">
                     <div class="post-header-line-1">
                     </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="post-body entry-content" id="post-body-1494707626336310316">
                     <div style="float: right; padding: 5px;">
                      <script src="http://www.stumbleupon.com/hostedbadge.php?s=5">
                      </script>
                     </div>
                     <div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;">
                      <a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-206bYyFa2co/VGwSRNSA5FI/AAAAAAAAPGc/muxTCagQRrw/s1600/LEGOLAND%2BDISOVERY%2BCENTER%2BWESTCHESTER%2BREVIEW%2BONE%2BSAVVY%2BMOM%2B24.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;">
                       <img border="0" height="480" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-206bYyFa2co/VGwSRNSA5FI/AAAAAAAAPGc/muxTCagQRrw/s1600/LEGOLAND%2BDISOVERY%2BCENTER%2BWESTCHESTER%2BREVIEW%2BONE%2BSAVVY%2BMOM%2B24.jpg" width="640"/>
                      </a>
                     </div>
                     <br/>
                     BRR!!! It's cold! It feels like the Winter has officially arrived here in the Northeast part of the country.You know what that means?
                     <i>
                      It's time to find indoor activities and outdoor winter sports/activities to keep the kids occupied.
                     </i>
                     <br/>
                     <br/>
                     If your looking for a fun indoor activity to do with the kids, head to LEGOLAND Discovery Center in Westchester. So much fun you guys! Our kids (as most kids their ages) are obsessed with all things LEGO. They can't get enough! They can build and build for hours on end.
                     <br/>
                     <br/>
                     We spent a day exploring at LEGOLAND Discovery center recently and I have to say, it's pretty amazing. When you step inside the bright entrance of LEGOLAND Discovery Center Westchester, be prepared to be amazed at every turn. Just walking through "Miniland" will leave you in awe! I definitely have a huge respect for the impressive creations in this exhibit and the builders behind them.
                     <br/>
                     <a name="more">
                     </a>
                     <br/>
                     <br/>
                     Take in the HUGE {lighted} models of New York City landmarks and other fun statues, or hop on one of the indoor rides (there are 2 at this location). You can also train to be a LEGO Master Builder! Kids can spend an hour in a LEGO Master Builder's class (there are several throughout the day) learning how to build the creation of the day with precision . After the class is over, kids can keep their creation with a small donation of $5. The donation benefits a local charity; the kids have a blast + it's for a great cause - it's a win-win for everyone!
                     <br/>
                     <br/>
                     Girl's will have a blast in the LEGO Friends area. They can partake in a little building fun or belt out a tune in the Karaoke station! The younger LEGO fans in training will delight in exploring the LEGO Duplo section, which boasts a large slide and a pit of giant foam LEGO Bricks! There's also a large play center in the center of it all for kids to climb and slide til' their hearts' content.
                     <br/>
                     <br/>
                     If you get hungry while you're there, no worries! There are so many healthy (affordable) options in the small food court inside of the Discovery Center. There are also several restaurants within a short walking distance just outside of the Discovery Center, as it's located in Ridge Hill.
                     <br/>
                     <br/>
                     <b>
                      All of this
                      <i>
                       and MORE
                      </i>
                      . Seriously, there's so much fun to be had at this place!
                     </b>
                     <br/>
                     <b>
                      <br/>
                     </b>
                     <b>
                      Check out our pics from our day at LEGOLAND Discovery Center Westchester below.
                     </b>

                     window.followersIframe = null;
    function followersIframeOpen(url) {
      gapi.load("gapi.iframes", function() {
        if (gapi.iframes &amp;&amp; gapi.iframes.getContext) {
          window.followersIframe = gapi.iframes.getContext().openChild({
            url: url,
            where: document.getElementById("followers-iframe-container"),
            messageHandlersFilter: gapi.iframes.CROSS_ORIGIN_IFRAMES_FILTER,
            messageHandlers: {
              '_ready': function(obj) {
                window.followersIframe.getIframeEl().height = obj.height;
              },
              'reset': function() {
                window.followersIframe.close();
                followersIframeOpen("https://www.blogger.com/followers.g?blogID\x3d2436705169879802526\x26origin\x3dhttp://www.onesavvymom.net/\x26colors\x3dCgt0cmFuc3BhcmVudBILdHJhbnNwYXJlbnQaBjU5NTk1OSIGMDAwMDAwKgZmZmZmZmYyBjkzOTM5MzoGNTk1OTU5QgYwMDAwMDBKBmY2ZjJmM1IGMDAwMDAwWgt0cmFuc3BhcmVudA%3D%3D\x26postID\x3d1494707626336310316");
              },
              'open': function(url) {
                window.followersIframe.close();
                followersIframeOpen(url);
              }
            }
          });
        }
      });
    }
    followersIframeOpen("https://www.blogger.com/followers.g?blogID\x3d2436705169879802526\x26origin\x3dhttp://www.onesavvymom.net/\x26colors\x3dCgt0cmFuc3BhcmVudBILdHJhbnNwYXJlbnQaBjU5NTk1OSIGMDAwMDAwKgZmZmZmZmYyBjkzOTM5MzoGNTk1OTU5QgYwMDAwMDBKBmY2ZjJmM1IGMDAwMDAwWgt0cmFuc3BhcmVudA%3D%3D\x26postID\x3d1494707626336310316");
